{"tid":1565373,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[行動][口號]915！銅鑼灣見！","createTime":"2019-09-13T06:22:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T10:41:52.000Z","uid":249705,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"73ecf4a5aec00bc9f1e972e2ac581c47ad02efe3","tid":1565373,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:22:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新口號</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">915！銅鑼灣見！</span></span><br />\n希望大家知道對面國家機器已經踩到上心口<br />\n一連串call馬唱国歌<br />\n就係想營造民意已經逆轉既形勢<br />\n我哋一定要用盡方法令更多人915出嚟<br />\n搶番個主動權<br />\n俾民意支持美國國會 去通過人權法案<br />\n<br />\n大家要繼續做文宣 派傳單 貼連儂牆<br />\n瘋狂喺FB IG Twitter repost<br />\n<br />\n希望今日中秋同聽日914遊行<br />\n會聽到大家叫新口號<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">915！銅鑼灣見！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4vFd19D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4vFd19D.jpg&h=6af2781c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/13/142057_4129c7cb7e9083ce67ee3eb80c394512.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F13%2F142057_4129c7cb7e9083ce67ee3eb80c394512.png&h=e89e0e78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yzi3EWE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYzi3EWE.png&h=2a7bc5ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K65p8P1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK65p8P1.png&h=b3878196&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TREa4on.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTREa4on.jpg&h=1cf625c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ytgppoo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fytgppoo.png&h=c8e7485f&s={SIZE}\" /><br 